"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[長文]中港婚姻：依足劇本發生喺自己屋企<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1023470/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1023470/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"00e458c4975631c9a52807f772c51e13b6a95f82","tid":1022991,"uid":124410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T05:15:29.000Z","msg":"林鄭縮埋一邊唔敢回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebf1caad87ee1ba3f297e6fa36a69c71960d654","tid":1022991,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:18:29.000Z","msg":"今日2點，旺角行人專用區亞皆老街起步，途經廣華醫院，旺角政府合署前空地作為終點。"},{"pid":"03fd5566e829d004b0ad07b6e2d4d5b53a31d306","tid":1022991,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:21:12.000Z","msg":"難得開始多人企出嚟<br />\n真係想知有幾多連登仔會去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d147b27e9d45fb075a5ec9c9f9e4c264845e85e6","tid":1022991,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:23:43.000Z","msg":"好揀唔揀揀今日<br />\n明知唔少人去馬拉松"},{"pid":"8e5f8104ffc52887ca3451ba8dc921bb38e1692d","tid":1022991,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更正</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日<span style=\"color: red;\">3點</span>，旺角行人專用區亞皆老街起步，途經廣華醫院，旺角政府合署前空地作為終點。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c06e015b7f6486bef390a4151a5ce4cf4118ff8","tid":1022991,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"香港地少蝗多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人出嚟發聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6aeccefd5bf4a9e85485a7637b6378803d5973","tid":1022991,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c06e015b7f6486bef390a4151a5ce4cf4118ff8","tid":1022991,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T17:02:25.000Z","msg":"香港地少蝗多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人出嚟發聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-07T17:03:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">而家先發現到???</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">5月11日 星期六 早上8點半<br />\n立法會將會開會討論有關修訂 暫未知會否表決 <br />\n由於秘書處政變 原本由涂謹申主持會議改為石禮謙主持<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人任何罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6df7766b9232783bef0dadd1d9e17244727adc09","tid":1022991,"uid":185022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd6aeccefd5bf4a9e85485a7637b6378803d5973","tid":1022991,"uid":113373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c06e015b7f6486bef390a4151a5ce4cf4118ff8","tid":1022991,"uid"